  "source": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n<title>Anti-Design / Maximalist</title>\n<script type=\"application/json\" id=\"effect-meta\">\n{\n  \"id\": \"anti-design\",\n  \"title\": \"Anti-Design / Maximalist\",\n  \"summary\": \"Intentional chaos: clashing system fonts, raw borders, overlapping rotated blocks, blinding color, and a marquee — anti-design as a statement.\",\n  \"description\": \"Anti-design (and its maximalist cousin) rejects polish on purpose — default fonts, visible structure, clashing colors, overlap, and 'ugly' energy used deliberately for personality. This page channels it for a zine/creative brand: a chaotic hero, a ransom-note grid, a marquee, and raw form controls — yet still readable and functional.\",\n  \"theme\": \"website-templates\",\n  \"categories\": [\"template\", \"experimental\", \"brand\"],\n  \"tags\": [\"anti-design\", \"maximalist\", \"brutalist\", \"raw\", \"zine\", \"experimental\", \"full-page\"],\n  \"tech\": [\"html\", \"css\"],\n  \"era\": \"2020s\",\n  \"difficulty\": \"beginner\",\n  \"dependencies\": [],\n  \"browser_support\": \"All browsers (deliberately simple).\",\n  \"performance_notes\": \"Mostly system fonts, borders, and one marquee. Extremely light by design.\",\n  \"accessibility_notes\": \"Chaos is visual, not structural: real heading order, sufficient text contrast on each block, focus-visible, and a reduced-motion guard for the marquee and any wobble. Use the aesthetic intentionally — it's not an excuse to skip a11y.\",\n  \"customization\": [\n    { \"name\": \"color blocks\", \"description\": \"Clashing section backgrounds\", \"default\": \"lime/pink/blue/yellow/black\" },\n    { \"name\": \"rotation\", \"description\": \"Per-block tilt\", \"default\": \"-3deg to 4deg\" }\n  ],\n  \"variations\": [\"Tone down to one clash color\", \"Add scanned-paper texture\", \"Swap to all-caps Courier everywhere\"],\n  \"related\": [\"neubrutalist-landing\", \"dopamine-brand\", \"retro-90s-homepage\"],\n  \"ai_usage\": \"Use for zines, art projects, music, fashion drops, and brands that want raw personality. The look = default fonts (Times/Courier/Arial mixed), thick black borders, clashing flat colors, slight rotations and overlap, and a marquee. Crucially keep it accessible: real heading order, contrast on each block, focus styles, reduced-motion guard. It's intentional ugliness, not broken markup.\"\n}\n</script>\n<style>\n  *{box-sizing:border-box}\n  body{margin:0;background:#f5f500;color:#000;font-family:Times New Roman,serif;line-height:1.3}\n  a{color:#0000ee}\n  .bar{background:#000;color:#fff;font-family:Courier New,monospace;padding:.4rem;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:.5rem;font-weight:bold}\n  .bar a{color:#f5f500}\n  .marq{background:#ff2bd6;color:#000;border-block:4px solid #000;overflow:hidden;white-space:nowrap;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-weight:900;text-transform:uppercase}\n  .marq span{display:inline-block;padding:.4rem 0;animation:m 14s linear infinite}\n  @keyframes m{to{transform:translateX(-50%)}}\n  .hero{padding:2rem;border-bottom:6px solid #000}\n  .hero h1{font-family:Arial Black,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:clamp(3rem,14vw,9rem);line-height:.82;margin:0;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:-.03em}\n  .hero h1 .a{background:#00e5ff;padding:0 .1em}.hero h1 .b{color:#ff2bd6;font-family:Courier New,monospace;font-style:italic}\n  .hero h1 .c{-webkit-text-stroke:3px #000;color:#f5f500}\n  .lede{font-family:Courier New,monospace;font-size:1.1rem;max-width:50ch;margin-top:1rem;background:#fff;border:3px solid #000;padding:.6rem;display:inline-block;transform:rotate(-1.5deg)}\n  .grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:0;border-bottom:6px solid #000}\n  .cell{border:3px solid #000;padding:1.4rem;min-height:160px}\n  .cell h2{font-family:Arial,sans-serif;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 .4rem;font-size:1.4rem}\n  .c1{background:#00e5ff;transform:rotate(0)}.c2{background:#ff2bd6;color:#fff}.c3{background:#fff}\n  .c4{background:#000;color:#c6ff3d;font-family:Courier New,monospace}.c5{background:#c6ff3d}.c6{background:#fff;transform:rotate(0)}\n  .cell.tilt{transform:rotate(2deg)}.cell.tilt2{transform:rotate(-2deg)}\n  .ransom{padding:2rem;border-bottom:6px solid #000;font-size:clamp(1.6rem,5vw,3rem);font-weight:900}\n  .ransom span{display:inline-block;padding:.1em .25em;margin:.1em;border:3px solid #000}\n  .r1{background:#ff2bd6;color:#fff;transform:rotate(-4deg);font-family:Courier New,monospace}\n  .r2{background:#00e5ff;transform:rotate(3deg);font-family:Times New Roman,serif}\n  .r3{background:#c6ff3d;transform:rotate(-2deg);font-family:Arial Black,sans-serif}\n  .r4{background:#000;color:#f5f500;transform:rotate(5deg)}\n  .signup{padding:2rem;background:#000;color:#fff;font-family:Courier New,monospace}\n  .signup input{font-family:inherit;font-size:1rem;padding:.6rem;border:3px solid #fff;background:#000;color:#fff}\n  .signup button{font-family:Arial Black,sans-serif;font-size:1rem;padding:.6rem 1.2rem;border:3px solid #fff;background:#c6ff3d;color:#000;cursor:pointer;text-transform:uppercase}\n  .signup button:hover{background:#ff2bd6;color:#fff}\n  a:focus-visible,button:focus-visible,input:focus-visible{outline:4px solid #00e5ff;outline-offset:2px}\n  footer{padding:1.2rem 2rem;font-family:Courier New,monospace;font-weight:bold;background:#f5f500}\n  @media(max-width:700px){.grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}\n  @media(prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){.marq span{animation:none;padding-left:0}.cell.tilt,.cell.tilt2,.lede,.ransom span{transform:none}}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"bar\"><span>★ NO-BRAND ZINE ISSUE #07 ★</span><span><a href=\"#\">SHOP</a> // <a href=\"#\">READ</a> // <a href=\"#\">ABOUT</a></span></div>\n  <div class=\"marq\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span>RULES ARE FAKE &nbsp;✶&nbsp; TASTE IS A SCAM &nbsp;✶&nbsp; MAKE IT LOUD &nbsp;✶&nbsp; RULES ARE FAKE &nbsp;✶&nbsp; TASTE IS A SCAM &nbsp;✶&nbsp; MAKE IT LOUD &nbsp;✶&nbsp;</span></div>\n\n  <header class=\"hero\">\n    <h1><span class=\"a\">WE</span> <span class=\"b\">don't</span><br><span class=\"c\">DO</span> NICE.</h1>\n    <p class=\"lede\">&gt; A zine about design that refuses to behave. Printed loud, shipped raw, zero apologies.</p>\n  </header>\n\n  <section class=\"grid\">\n    <div class=\"cell c1\"><h2>Issue #07</h2><p>64 pages of clashing fonts and strong opinions.</p></div>\n    <div class=\"cell c2 tilt\"><h2>Sold out twice</h2><p>Restocked. Again. Grab it before it's gone.</p></div>\n    <div class=\"cell c3\"><h2>By 14 weirdos</h2><p>Designers, poets, and one very angry typographer.</p></div>\n    <div class=\"cell c4\">&gt; print &gt; chaos &gt;<br>&gt; repeat();</div>\n    <div class=\"cell c5 tilt2\"><h2>$12</h2><p>Or free if you can argue with us and win.</p></div>\n    <div class=\"cell c6\"><h2>Worldwide</h2><p>We ship the mess everywhere. <a href=\"#\">Where?</a></p></div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"ransom\">\n    <span class=\"r1\">GET</span><span class=\"r2\">THE</span><span class=\"r3\">WHOLE</span><span class=\"r4\">MESS</span>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"signup\">\n    <h2 style=\"font-family:Arial Black,sans-serif;text-transform:uppercase\">Join the noise</h2>\n    <form onsubmit=\"event.preventDefault();this.querySelector('button').textContent='YOU’RE IN'\">\n      <label>EMAIL&gt; <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"you@wherever.net\" required aria-label=\"Email\"></label>\n      <button type=\"submit\">SUBSCRIBE</button>\n    </form>\n  </section>\n\n  <footer>© <span id=\"yr\"></span> NO-BRAND ZINE // made with spite &amp; a text editor</footer>\n  <script>document.getElementById('yr').textContent=new Date().getFullYear();</script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"
